-- Riyad Bank's Second-Quarter Net Income Declines 17% to $204 Million
-- Glen Carey
-- 2010-07-10T06:14:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-10/riyad-bank-s-second-quarter-profit-declines-16-5-to-766-million-riyals.html

          
          
             Riyad Bank said second-quarter
profit declined to 766 million riyals from 918 million riyals in
the year-earlier period, according to a statement on the Saudi
bourse website today.  
